# Rust/native thumbnail build artifacts
# 默认忽略 Rust target 与构建缓存，仅保留最终交付产物
freeassetfilter/core/native/thumbnail_rust/target/*
freeassetfilter/core/native/thumbnail_rust/.cargo/

# 保留 Cargo.lock 以便稳定复现、一键编译
!freeassetfilter/core/native/thumbnail_rust/Cargo.lock

# 保留可直接运行的预编译 DLL（main.py 可直接调用）
!freeassetfilter/core/native/thumbnail_generator.dll
!freeassetfilter/core/native/opencv_world4120.dll
!freeassetfilter/core/native/opencv_videoio_ffmpeg4130_64.dll

# 只放行 release 最终产物文件，不放行构建过程产物与缓存
!freeassetfilter/core/native/thumbnail_rust/target/release/
freeassetfilter/core/native/thumbnail_rust/target/release/*
!freeassetfilter/core/native/thumbnail_rust/target/release/thumbnail_generator.dll
!freeassetfilter/core/native/thumbnail_rust/target/release/thumbnail_generator.dll.lib
!freeassetfilter/core/native/thumbnail_rust/target/release/thumbnail_generator.dll.exp
!freeassetfilter/core/native/thumbnail_rust/target/release/thumbnail_generator.pdb

